{"author":{"id":"b78c39e7b13f90a5827abfba043255fe7a4ede1499df23f110fffe5abfa44adc"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1769629711,"nonce":"Z4PnHsmq2SoEr80Cb/rYQ17O7MI=","metadata":{"github-id":"I_kwDOQ241x87mf1To","github-url":"https://github.com/rolker/ros2_agent_workspace/issues/108","origin":"github"},"title":"Add testing workflow commands to CLI_COMMANDS.md","message":"## Problem\nThere are no documented testing workflows in `.agent/CLI_COMMANDS.md`. Agents must figure out `colcon test` flags themselves, leading to:\n- Long hangs without output visibility\n- Inconsistent test invocation\n- Wasted time debugging test execution\n\n## Example Friction\n```bash\n# Agent runs this (no output for 2+ minutes):\ncolcon test --packages-select helm_manager\n\n# Should have run:\ncolcon test --packages-select helm_manager --event-handlers console_direct+\n```\n\n## Proposed Solution\nAdd testing commands to `.agent/CLI_COMMANDS.md`:\n\n### `/test`\n**Script**: `.agent/scripts/test_package.sh`\n- Run tests for current package\n- Shows output in real-time\n- Includes test-result summary\n\n### `/test-all`\n**Script**: `.agent/scripts/test_all.sh`\n- Run all tests across workspaces\n- Proper event handlers for output\n- Summary of pass/fail counts\n- Flag to continue on failure\n\n### `/test-package \u003cname\u003e`\n**Script**: `.agent/scripts/test_package.sh \u003cname\u003e`\n- Test specific package by name\n- Real-time output\n- Test result summary\n\n## Implementation Details\n\nRecommended colcon flags:\n```bash\ncolcon test \\\n  --packages-select \u003cpackage\u003e \\\n  --event-handlers console_direct+ \\\n  --return-code-on-test-failure\n\ncolcon test-result --verbose\n```\n\n## Impact\n- ✅ Agents can run tests efficiently\n- ✅ Consistent test execution across agents\n- ✅ Faster feedback (no more 2min hangs)\n- ✅ Critical for testing strategy implementation (Issues #22-33)\n\n## Priority\n🟡 Medium-High - Needed for upcoming testing work (12 sub-issues depend on this)\n\n## Session Evidence\nSession: 66b4eea3-8aff-4a81-88b6-6aafd77a65e3\n- Ran `colcon test` directly, hung for 2+ minutes with minimal output\n- Had to poll 6 times with read_bash before stopping\n- Eventually used `colcon build` instead to verify changes\n- Testing workflow would have saved 5+ minutes\n\n---\n**🤖 Reported-By**: Copilot CLI Agent (Claude Sonnet 4.5)","files":null}]}